Subject: drm/xlnx: Use drm_module_platform_driver() to register the driver
Git-commit: fad5453444fd95fb63e3cb6033c2489b6d9f4f14
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

The macro calls to a DRM specific platform driver init handler that checks
whether the driver is allowed to be registered or not.

Signed-off-by: Javier Martinez Canillas <javierm@redhat.com>
Acked-by: Daniel Vetter <daniel.vetter@ffwll.ch>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20211217003752.3946210-21-javierm@redhat.com
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/xlnx/zynqmp_dpsub.c | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/xlnx/zynqmp_dpsub.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/xlnx/zynqmp_dpsub.c
index ac37053412a1..824b510e337b 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/xlnx/zynqmp_dpsub.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/xlnx/zynqmp_dpsub.c
@@ -25,6 +25,7 @@
 #include <drm/drm_gem_framebuffer_helper.h>
 #include <drm/drm_managed.h>
 #include <drm/drm_mode_config.h>
+#include <drm/drm_module.h>
 #include <drm/drm_probe_helper.h>
 #include <drm/drm_vblank.h>
 
@@ -286,7 +287,7 @@ static struct platform_driver zynqmp_dpsub_driver = {
 	},
 };
 
-module_platform_driver(zynqmp_dpsub_driver);
+drm_module_platform_driver(zynqmp_dpsub_driver);
 
 MODULE_AUTHOR("Xilinx, Inc.");
 MODULE_DESCRIPTION("ZynqMP DP Subsystem Driver");
